lease.com<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2012-06-11</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AModern+language&amp;rft.btitle=Most+Studied+Foreign+Languages+in+the+U.S.+%E2%80%94&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.pub=Infoplease.com&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.infoplease.com%2Fipa%2FA0905275.html&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1255\nCached time: 20170808140621\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.156 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.209 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1019/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\xe2\x80\x90expand include size: 21657/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2038/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 11/40\nExpensive parser function count: 6/500\nLua time usage: 0.083/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 3.28 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  178.787      1 -total\n 32.73%   58.515      1 Template:Reflist\n 18.05%   32.270      3 Template:Fix\n 16.62%   29.709      1 Template:Cite_book\n 16.56%   29.603      1 Template:Refimprove\n 16.10%   28.779      4 Template:Delink\n 14.07%   25.164      1 Template:Ambox\n 13.82%   24.716      1 Template:Clarification_needed\n 12.15%   21.725      2 Template:Citation_needed\n 12.10%   21.629      1 Template:Redirect\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2672429-0!canonical and timestamp 20170808140621 and revision id 794036253\n -->\n<noscript><img src="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:CentralAutoLogin/start?type=1x1" alt="" title="" width="1" height="1" style="border: none; position: absolute;" /></noscript></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class="printfooter">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from "<a dir="ltr" href="https://en.wikipedia.